name: AGTMNS: A Game That Makes No Sense
overview: If we could make sense of this game, we would have named it something else. This is all I can tell you, it is barely a platformer. There are undies and you must gather them. Avoid the things that are not undies. Get to the next level if you can, there are more skivvies there. Step 1: Gather the briefs Step 2: ??? Step 3: Profit!!
